<p>&nbsp;Pricing in 2026 continues to vary based on technique, clinic reputation, graft count, and additional services such as accommodation and transfers. For example, FUE procedures in Turkey may range from €1600 to €2700, while more advanced techniques like DHI or Sapphire FUE can cost more. Larger procedures involving 6000 grafts may range from $2,100 to $4,900. Overall, patients can expect to pay between $2,000 and $8,000 for a complete package, which often includes hotel stays and transportation.</p>
